INVINCIBLE is an adult animated superhero series that revolves around 17-year-old Mark Grayson, whos just like every other guy his age except his father is the most powerful superhero on the planet, Omni-Man. But as Mark develops powers of his own, he discovers his fathers legacy may not be as heroic as it seems.
